        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='28545' id='19' type-v2='text' w='34100' x='57800' y='22818'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#75a1c7' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>The </run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#75a1c7' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>monthly sales trend</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#75a1c7' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> shows relatively </run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#75a1c7' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>low and fluctuating sales during the first half of the year</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#75a1c7' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>, with a noticeable dip around February and April. Sales begin to </run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#75a1c7' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>rise steadily from September</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#75a1c7' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>, reaching a </run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#75a1c7' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>peak in November</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#75a1c7' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>, followed by a </run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#75a1c7' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>decline in December</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#75a1c7' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>. Overall, the data indicates </run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#75a1c7' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>strong growth toward the end of the year with a seasonal peak in November</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
